Usage
=======

$ ./hadamard_test.py -h
usage: hadamard_test.py [-h] [-n N] [--phi {random,one,zero}]

Hadamard test

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -n N                  size of the unitary matrix (default=2)
  --phi {random,one,zero}
                        input vector selection (default=random)


Sample Run
============
$ ./hadamard_test.py -n 4



Notes
=======
Result will be printed to standard output, intermediates will be printed to
standard error. Printing of matrices and vectors uses the numpy defaults, some
elements may be omitted depending the sizes.
